'''Plastifoam''' was a packing material used in the kitchen of [[Jabba's Palace/Legends|Jabba's Palace]].

==History==
The [[Gamorrean/Legends|Gamorrean]] [[Gartogg/Legends|Gartogg]] consumed handfuls of the substance thinking it was food.<ref name="And Then There Were Some: The Gamorrean Guard's Tale">{{StoryCite|story=And Then There Were Some: The Gamorrean Guard's Tale|book=Tales from Jabba's Palace}}</ref>

